==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Provisional
<hw>Pro*vi"sion*al</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[Cf. F.
<ets>provisionnel</ets>.]</ety> <def>Of the nature of a provision;
serving as a provision for the time being; -- used of partial or
temporary arrangements; <as>as, a <ex>provisional</ex> government; a
<ex>provisional</ex> treaty.</as></def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Provisionally</ent>⟦br⟧
